<title>msẖ llʿạlm</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 misẖ̊ lil̊ʿālam̊
 ạảnaạ walạ yum̊kin̊ ạảḥ̊yaạ
 (ʿum̊rī fī yūm̊ mā hakūn̊ ạảbadāaⁿ
 min̊ raʿāyāh)2 ạảnaạ mit̊gẖarãb̊
 fīh lakin̊ misẖ̊ juwãạh (ạảnā mit̊gẖarãb̊
 ʿan̊duh sākin̊ qal̊b̊ ạllh)2
 (sikĩtiy
 juwãạyaạ hiyã ạl̊waṭan̊ riḥ̊litiy
 baḥ̊yāhaạ fuwq̊ ạlzãman̊)2 (ʿan̊d̊ ṣalībak̊ yā ạib̊n̊ ạllh ạit̊ṣalab̊
 ạl̊ʿālam̊ līã)2 (wibaqayt̊ lil̊ʿaạlam̊ maṣ̊luwb̊)2</lyrics>
</song>